# Overview

You are a senior TypeScript engineer.

Build src/core/statistics/subjectStats.ts.

Purpose:
Generate statistics per exam subject.

Input:
- SubjectScore {
    subjectId: string;
    score: number;
  }

Output per subject:
- average score
- min score
- max score
- count

Export function generateSubjectStats().

Rules:
- Group by subjectId
- Round results to 2 decimals
- Ignore null values
- Pure logic only
